entries.title_d: Remain in the Endor system and deliver the Rebel plans to a command shuttle. A shuttle will meet you in the Endor system to receive the Rebel plans from you.
entries.title: Endor System: Deliver the Rebel Plans to Command
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the arrival location of the shuttle and wait for it to arrive.
entries.quest_location_d: The shuttle will meet you in the Endor system.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the shuttle and transfer the plans to command. Once you have completed this task return to your commander for further instructions.
entries.hello_d: Hello, pilot. We can begin the data transfer whenever you are ready.
entries.found_loc_d: Transfer data to location. A shuttle will meet you there to pick up the data.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Beginning download now. Please stand by.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Download completed. Nice work pilot. Your superior officer requests that you speak with him.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Maintain your current position. The command shuttle will be arriving shortly to take the data.
